skdetail:

Invocation Name: take a minute
des: Accomplish something in sixty seconds or less! Whether it is taking out the trash, doing ten push-ups, or silently meditating, if you have only a minute, you can make it a productive one.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
